articles.title: The P7 peptide antagonizes bFGF-induced malignant behaviors of ovarian cancer by inhibiting MEK/ERK signaling pathway.
articles.summary: P7 peptide blocks bFGF's ability to promote ovarian cancer growth and spread by interrupting a key molecular signaling pathway.

articles.title: Test: Breakthrough in Lung Cancer Treatment
articles.summary: A new targeted therapy successfully treated 60% of advanced lung cancer patients with specific genetic mutations, offering hope for improved outcomes.
